Detektif Sullivan?

757
00:41:22,836 --> 00:41:25,220
Sully?

758
00:41:25,222 --> 00:41:28,006
Ini aku, Car...

759
00:41:28,008 --> 00:41:32,227
Oh, tidak.

760
